Ramiel:
It is hard to explain. The timeline has been deviated, and it is our 
duty to make up for this. Your help will be needed for this.

Gogolan:
By the way, our ship has detected a form of weaponry on you. We would 
like you to hide it in the forest so that no one will feel threatened 
for the conference.

The scan is executed on Ramiel and Gogolan. The scan reveals unknown 
weaponry, unknown mechanisms, unknown armor and energy signature 
seemingly fused between maximal and predacons.
